trans-unit.source: Defines the settings for a peer resolver service.
Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.ServiceModel.PeerResolvers.PeerResolverSettings"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initierar en ny instans av den <xref href="System.ServiceModel.PeerResolvers.PeerResolverSettings"> </xref> klass.

trans-unit.source: Gets the specific settings for a custom peer resolver.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar de specifika inställningarna för en anpassad peer-matchare.

trans-unit.source: This property is set only if <xref:System.ServiceModel.PeerResolvers.PeerResolverSettings.Mode%2A> is set to <xref:System.ServiceModel.PeerResolvers.PeerResolverMode>.
trans-unit.target: Den här egenskapen anges bara om <xref:System.ServiceModel.PeerResolvers.PeerResolverSettings.Mode%2A>anges till <xref:System.ServiceModel.PeerResolvers.PeerResolverMode>.</xref:System.ServiceModel.PeerResolvers.PeerResolverMode> </xref:System.ServiceModel.PeerResolvers.PeerResolverSettings.Mode%2A>

trans-unit.source: <xref href="System.ServiceModel.PeerResolvers.PeerCustomResolverSettings"></xref> that contains the settings and resolver instance for the associated custom peer resolver service.
trans-unit.target: <xref href="System.ServiceModel.PeerResolvers.PeerCustomResolverSettings"></xref>som innehåller de inställningar och matcharen instans för den tillhörande anpassade peer lösartjänsten.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets whether the peer resolver instance associated with this service is either PNRP-specific, a custom resolver, or automatically determined.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar eller anger om peer-matcharen instansen som är associerade med den här tjänsten är antingen PNRP-specifik anpassade lösaren, eller automatiskt.

trans-unit.source: <xref href="System.ServiceModel.PeerResolvers.PeerResolverMode"></xref> enumeration value that specifies the mode of the peer resolver service.
Gets or sets the specific referral policy used by the peer resolver service.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar eller anger den specifika hänvisning principen används av peer-lösartjänsten.

trans-unit.source: <xref href="System.ServiceModel.PeerResolvers.PeerReferralPolicy"></xref> that specifies whether peer referrals are shared or not.
trans-unit.target: <xref href="System.ServiceModel.PeerResolvers.PeerReferralPolicy"></xref>som anger om peer hänvisningar ska delas eller inte.
